stimulus:
Welcome! This is the second day of the experiment. This part will last ~30 minutes.


Just as a reminder, you are the head captain of a pirate ship traveling around the world to different places.

Today,you’ve arrived at the final destination of your journey!

Unfortunately, it’s very foggy out, so you won’t be able to see it in the distance like the places you visited yesterday.

You’ll still be deciding which pirates you want to rob ships. Because of the fog, however, you won't be able to see which ship your chosen pirate is robbing.

[Press the space bar to go over the instructions]

Like yesterday,as the head captain of the ship, you have one important things to do:

Pick the pirate who you think will be most successful at robbing the next ship.

This is important in determining how much bonus money you’ll win.


The game will start by showing you the pirates. First pick a pirate using the 1, 2, 3 buttons on your keyboard.

Press '1' to choose red beard, '2' to choose white beard, and '3' to choose black beard

You only have 3 seconds to pick a pirate, so please make a choice quickly! If you are too slow, you’ll have to wait a bit during the time out.

Don’t feel rushed, but please do try to make a choice every time.

How good a pirate is at robbing a ship will change depending on the place they are in and how good the defenses are of the ship.

[Press the space bar to begin the practice game]

Unlike yesterday, sometimes you’ll be asked if you’ve seen a ship before (see the example below). You will use the 5, 6, 7, 8 buttons on your keyboard to respond.

If you definitely did not see the ship, pick the the big red thumbs down by pressing 5.

If you don’t think you saw it but aren’t sure, then pick the small red thumbs down by pressing 6.

If you think you might have seen it, then pick the small green thumbs up by pressing 7.

If you definitely did see this ship before, then pick the big thumb green thumbs up by pressing 8.

If you recall it correctly, then you’ll get a gold coin!

[Press the space bar to the experiment]

You are all done with both parts of the experiment! You made $15 plus $3 in bonus payment!! Thank you for participating. You will recieve your payment within 3 days

[Press the space bar to end the experiment]
